    {
      "name": "UnlockedFormulaCells",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果该值为 <strong>True</strong>（默认值），则 ET 将识别未锁定并包含一个公式的选定单元格。如果该值为 <strong>False</strong>，则禁用包含公式的未锁定单元格的错误检查。<strong>Boolean</strong> 类型，可读写。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例中，“自动更正选项”按钮出现在单元格 A3 旁，该单元格是一个包含公式的未锁定单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ErrorCheckingOptions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">UnlockedFormulaCells</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A2&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value2</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A3&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Formula</span> = <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;=A1+A2&quot;</span>\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Range</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;A3&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Locked</span> = <span class=\"hljs-literal\">false</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例显示 ET 是否识别未锁定并包含一个公式的选定单元格。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ErrorCheckingOptions</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">UnlockedFormulaCells</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
